Closed For The Season (Carnival of Fear) - Trapped in a forgotten amusement park, a young woman (Kristy) finds herself terrorized by the living memories of the park. She must break free from the park's grasp before she becomes its next victim.
2010.  Stars: Aimee Brooks, Damian Maffei, Joe Unger
